(136, 1, '2023-09-07 09:40:44', '2023-09-07 09:40:44', '<em><strong>- Child Rights Expert</strong></em>\r\n\r\nMr. Pradhan has been associated with CWIN since 1991 and has worked through the years for the promotion and protection of children at risk. Mr. Pradhan is also the Chairperson of Children as zones of peace - National Alliance (CZOPP) and MenEngage Alliance.\r\nEd: Masters in Business Administration', 'Mr. Madhav Pradhan', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mr-madhav-pradhan', '', '', '2023-09-07 09:40:44', '2023-09-07 09:40:44', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=team&#038;p=136', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(137, 1, '2023-09-07 09:41:18', '2023-09-07 09:41:18', '<em><strong>- Women’s Rights Expert and Founding associate of CWIN-Nepal.</strong></em>\r\n\r\nMs. Joshi is a women’s rights defender and has been working in Nepal Bank Ltd. For the past 25 years. Ed: Masters in Commerce', 'Ms. Sumitra Joshi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ms-sumitra-joshi', '', '', '2023-09-07 09:41:18', '2023-09-07 09:41:18', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=team&#038;p=137', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(138, 1, '2023-09-07 09:41:46', '2023-09-07 09:41:46', '<em><strong>- Child Rights Expert (Ex. Officio representing management)</strong></em>\r\n\r\nMs. Tuladhar is a founding associate of CWIN and is an expert on various child protection issues including trafficking, street children, CSEC, child participation, children and conflict transformation and online child protection. Ms. Tuladhar is also a founding member of AATWIN and Shanti Malika. Ed: Masters in English Literature', 'Ms. Sumnima Tuladhar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ms-sumnima-tuladhar', '', '', '2023-09-07 09:41:59', '2023-09-07 09:41:59', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=team&#038;p=138', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(139, 1, '2023-09-07 09:42:24', '2023-09-07 09:42:24', '<em><strong>- Management Expert</strong></em>\r\n\r\nMr. Shrestha has been associated with CWIN for more than two decades. He is also Director at Capital FM. Ed: Masters in Commerce.', 'Mr. Subodh Shrestha', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mr-subodh-shrestha', '', '', '2023-09-07 09:42:24', '2023-09-07 09:42:24', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=team&#038;p=139', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(140, 1, '2023-09-07 09:42:52', '2023-09-07 09:42:52', '<em><strong>- Anthropologist</strong></em>\r\n\r\nMr. Limbu has done a number of researches and teaches Medical Anthropology at Tribhuwan University. He is also associated with Friends for Peace. Ed: Masters in Anthropology', 'Mr. Tanka Limbu', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mr-tanka-limbu', '', '', '2023-09-07 09:42:52', '2023-09-07 09:42:52', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=team&#038;p=140', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(141, 1, '2023-09-07 09:43:21', '2023-09-07 09:43:21', '<em><strong>- Research Expert</strong></em>\r\n\r\nProf. Subedi is a well-known expert in labour research and has carried out national research studies for ILO and the government of Nepal. Prof. Subedi is also the Senate Member of Tribhuwan University. Ed: PhD/Population Studies', 'Prof. Dr. Govind Subedi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prof-dr-govind-subedi', '', '', '2023-09-07 09:43:21', '2023-09-07 09:43:21', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=team&#038;p=141', 0, 'team', '', 0),
