(902, 1, '2023-09-13 07:01:18', '2023-09-13 07:01:18', '13th September 2023, Kathmandu.\r\n\r\nAdolescents and Youth participants discussed the existing situation of online abuse and exploitation, legal provisions, and required amendments in them to keep children safe online. In the workshop titled \"Children and Adolescents\' Workshop on Preventing ad Responding to Online Sexual Exploitaion of Children (Down to Zero: Stepping up Fight against Sexual Exploitation of Children) \" was organized by CWIN- Nepal in support of Terres des Hommes Netherlands. The workshop was attended by Social Mobilizers, Youth Change Makers, and Peer educator, members of National Adolescent Girls\' Network and Boys\' Network and representatives of child clubs. The participants discussed in group about their concerns to be addressed in the16th periodic plan by the government to keep the children safe online and to ensure the rights of children.', 'Children and Adolescents\' Workshop on Preventing ad Responding to Online Sexual Exploitation of Children (Down to Zero: Stepping up Fight against Sexual Exploitation of Children)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'children-and-adolescents-workshop-on-preventing-ad-responding-to-online-sexual-exploitation-of-children-down-to-zero-stepping-up-fight-against-sexual-exploitation-of-children', '', '', '2023-09-14 07:02:18', '2023-09-14 07:02:18', '', 0, 'https://cwin.org.np/new/?post_type=news&#038;p=902', 0, 'news', '', 0),
